            <span style="font-weight:500">Welcome!</span> I’m a professional software engineer and technology consultant with extensive experience in the Microsoft .NET tech stack.
        </MudText>

        <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Style="font-size:1.5em;font-weight:200;" GutterBottom="true">
            Starting as a desktop developer, I’ve since transitioned into full-stack web development,
            where I’ve worked as a developer, team lead, and consultant.
            My background as a former non-commissioned officer in the United States Army instilled in me
            the principles of servant leadership, which I bring to each project to help solve complex technical challenges.
        </MudText>

        <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Style="font-size:1em;font-weight:100;" GutterBottom="true">
            To contact me, visit my <MudLink Href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/cshaw79" Target="_blank">LinkedIn profile</MudLink>.
            If you're interested in jiu-jitsu, follow me on <MudLink Href="https://www.instagram.com/cshawbjj/" Target="_blank">Instagram</MudLink>.
        </MudText>

        <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Style="font-size:1em;font-weight:100;">
            This site was developed using <MudLink Href="https://dotnet.microsoft.com/en-us/apps/aspnet/web-apps/blazor" Target="_blank">Blazor WebAssembly</MudLink>,
            <MudLink Href="https://mudblazor.com/" Target="_blank">MudBlazor</MudLink>,
            and <MudLink Href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/core/whats-new/dotnet-9/overview" Target="_blank">.NET 9</MudLink>.
            The source code is available on <MudLink Href="https://github.com/cms79/resume" Target="_blank">GitHub</MudLink>.
